index.html <!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>For My Rasmalyii</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff9a9e, #fecfef);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 400px;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ff4d88;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #444;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .heart {
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="card">
    <h1>For My Rasmalyii 💗</h1>
    
    <p>
        You are one of the most comfortable and positive people in my life.
        I genuinely feel lucky to have you.
    </p>

    <p>
        I hope I am someone you can always talk to freely.
        No matter what happens, I will always support you and stand by you.
    </p>

    <p>
        Stay happy, stay confident, and keep shining ✨
    </p>

    <div class="heart">🤍</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
